1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,660
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:38,060
Episode 18

3
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:41,900
Mr. Chen.

4
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:45,820
Don’t make mistakes again

5
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:49,700
on the stage.

6
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:55,259
Rest assured.

7
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:57,259
You will

8
00:01:58,740 --> 00:01:59,900
be satisfied.

9
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,820
Mr. Shang.

10
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:34,100
Stop cracking melon seeds

11
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:35,579
like clock ticking.

12
00:02:36,579 --> 00:02:38,660
None of your business.

13
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:43,700
How come you are so nervous when rehearing operas?

14
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,460
I may lose my job.

15
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,620
Of course I’m nervous.

16
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:52,260
I’ve got the headline for the tomorrow.

17
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,340
Liu Hanyun denounced Chen Renxiang.

18
00:02:55,579 --> 00:02:56,940
A famous star from Peking

19
00:02:58,300 --> 00:02:59,460
lost in Nanjing.

20
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:02,380
You’re laughing?

21
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:06,940
Not that serious.

22
00:03:07,380 --> 00:03:09,260
I’ve been performing Peking Opera these years.

23
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:13,060
I forgot the tune of Kun opera long ago.

24
00:03:13,780 --> 00:03:14,940
Let me teach you now.

25
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,540
My master.

26
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:18,540
Don’t make fun of me. OK?

27
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:19,780
I’m about to perform.

28
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:20,420
You teach me now.

29
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:21,500
I have no time to learn, do I?

30
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,220
How about...

31
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:26,220
What?

32
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:27,620
You sing and I perform.

33
00:03:27,620 --> 00:03:28,540
No.

34
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,940
That’s fake and deceitful.

35
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:31,860
No.

36
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:34,740
Shang Xirui. If I lose today,

37
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:37,060
you are also guilty.

38
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,940
You are not capable enough.

39
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:40,220
How come you blame me?

40
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:41,940
Hadn’t you come to Nanking halfway,

41
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:43,940
I’d have gone to the park with my girlfriend.

42
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:46,380
Would I have to perform here?

43
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:49,620
Look at the opera Liu Hanyun ordered,

44
00:03:49,620 --> 00:03:51,220
Chaoyuan Song.

45
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:52,820
Isn’t it Jade Hairpin

46
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:54,579
you performed on the boat then?

47
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:56,300
You made this trouble, didn’t you?

48
00:03:59,620 --> 00:04:01,340
You think I can’t deal with you?

49
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:04,020
You want a fight?

50
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:06,820
Shang Xirui.

51
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:13,220
Mr. Shang.

52
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,339
Master Shang.

53
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,620
Please.

54
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:23,180
Save me. Save me.

55
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:26,700
Please! Save me!

56
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:33,300
Please! I beg you!

57
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,220
Save me! Save me!

58
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:35,580
Save me! Save me! Save me!

59
00:04:39,060 --> 00:05:06,140
♫ Heart is like cloud and water ♫

60
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:31,740
♫ No unnecessary worries ♫

61
00:05:34,700 --> 00:06:01,300
♫ Spring is coming ♫

62
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:06,380
OK.

63
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:09,100
The voice is delicate.

64
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:10,780
I can tell that

65
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:13,700
you've studied the melody conscientiously.

66
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,660
It’s rare to hear this now.

67
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,260
I’m flattered, Mr. Liu.

68
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:31,700
Mr. Liu.

69
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:56,180
Mr. Liu.

70
00:06:58,380 --> 00:06:59,820
One is on the stage.

71
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,980
The other is behind the stage.

72
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:03,980
You performed in a pair

73
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:05,820
and fooled

74
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:08,500
this old man.

75
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,300
Mr. Liu.

76
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:10,780
It's my bad idea.

77
00:07:11,460 --> 00:07:12,500
Don't blame Mr. Shang.

78
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:17,820
You think I can be

79
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:19,780
easily deceived?

80
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:23,340
You cooperated well,

81
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:27,180
but actors’ voicesare different.

82
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:30,740
I found it out as soon as Mr. Chen performed.

83
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:35,540
Sir, your ears are keen.

84
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:37,700
I can’t hide anything from you.

85
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:41,780
Mr. Shang.

86
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:44,340
Could it be that

87
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:48,140
you’re Xirui, the well-known performer in Peking?

88
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,540
Your voice

89
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:55,020
is quite like Mr. Ning Jiulang’s style.

90
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,300
You are right, sir.

91
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,060
I studied opera from Jiulang.

92
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,860
Are you Jiulang's apprentice?

93
00:08:02,020 --> 00:08:03,060
Not exactly.

94
00:08:03,540 --> 00:08:04,940
He doesn’t allow me to call him master.

95
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:11,780
Mr. Ning is still stubborn as ever.

96
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:14,060
It was you on the boat that day, right?

97
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,340
Yes.

98
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:20,180
Why did you perform Kun opera?

99
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:22,180
Now few people perform

100
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:24,140
Kun opera in Jiangnan.

101
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:25,700
That’s why I performed

102
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:27,780
on a whim.

103
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:32,260
Ning Jiulang said

104
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:34,220
Kun opera nurtures people.

105
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,980
Jiangnan’s elegant rhyme

106
00:08:38,299 --> 00:08:39,500
makes you have the spirit

107
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,780
against the mainstream.

108
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:45,460
Eat dinner here.

109
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,700
All my children will be present.

110
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:48,380
Gentlemen.

111
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:50,140
You may join us.

112
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:53,100
Thank you for your hospitality, Mr. Liu.

113
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:56,180
Quite like Jiulang’s style.

114
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:32,260
Brother.

115
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,180
What do you think of my dress?

116
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:35,260
Does it fit?

117
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:38,860
Beautiful.

118
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:41,420
My sister is a graceful beauty now.

119
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:44,860
Brother.

120
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:48,860
Have you decided how to tell Mrs. Cheng?

121
00:09:49,940 --> 00:09:50,940
Not yet.

122
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:53,980
Things come one after another.

123
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:57,260
I haven’t had time to make up with her.

124
00:09:58,020 --> 00:09:59,460
I don’t think so.

125
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:01,980
You just feel guilty

126
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,060
and avoid the trouble.

127
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,860
Is your sister-in-law a trouble?

128
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:06,780
Yes.

129
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:08,540
It’s one thing.

130
00:10:08,940 --> 00:10:10,700
When it comes to you and her,

131
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,420
you are not talking about the same thing.

132
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:17,540
I wish my sister-in-law can be generous

133
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:19,100
and show mercy.

134
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:22,100
You still need me

135
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:25,180
to deal with the trouble of your sister-in-law.

136
00:10:26,140 --> 00:10:28,020
OK. Tell me then.

137
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:29,700
How will you deal with me?

138
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:45,300
It’s a family dinner.

139
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:47,460
Make yourself at home.

140
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:51,380
They are my godsons.

141
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:56,500
Let me introduce these two gentlemen.

142
00:10:57,420 --> 00:11:00,460
The famous performer from Peking,

143
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:02,540
Mr. Shang Xirui.

144
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:04,140
Chen Renxiang.

145
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:05,260
Mr. Chen.

146
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:06,860
-Mr. Chen.
-Mr. Chen.

147
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:09,860
You may take care of each other

148
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:10,820
in the future.

149
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:12,700
Yes, father.

150
00:11:13,180 --> 00:11:14,540
I know Mr. Chen.

151
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,100
Do you remember me?

152
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:18,500
When I gave a speech in Peking back then,

153
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:20,460
I watched your Ascension to Throne.

154
00:11:20,460 --> 00:11:22,700
Minister Li. Of course, I remember you.

155
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:28,460
It’s a pity I haven’t watched Mr. Shang’s opera.

156
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:29,300
I have.

157
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:31,180
But I am just a small businessman.

158
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:33,460
I don’t think Mr. Shang recognizes me.

159
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:35,580
You are modest.

160
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:38,580
My brother runs the biggest soap factory in China.

161
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:40,500
You must have used his soap.

162
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:42,900
You’re flattering me, gentlemen.

163
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:46,340
Alright. No more talk.

164
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:49,100
The food gets cold. Let’s eat.

165
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:51,900
Please.

166
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:53,620
Please. Here.

167
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:30,900
Is this the way you deal with me?

168
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:32,980
I knew

169
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:35,100
you would mistake it

170
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:36,340
if I give you now.

171
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:39,140
I specially picked it for you

172
00:12:39,140 --> 00:12:41,100
from the safe in the morning.

173
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:43,020
Keep it for yourself.

174
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,380
Don’t give it to your cousins.

175
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,940
Chacha’er has grown up.

176
00:12:58,580 --> 00:13:00,300
Do you worry to let her go to school?

177
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:02,420
When I was fourteen,

178
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:04,380
I had gone to Britain to study.

179
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:05,980
Boys can travel around the world.

180
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:07,220
She is a girl.

181
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:08,380
So what?

182
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:11,220
There were also girls in my school abroad,

183
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:12,460
even in the department of mathematics,

184
00:13:12,620 --> 00:13:15,060
while I studied liberal arts.

185
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:17,340
I learned English at home,

186
00:13:17,780 --> 00:13:19,780
yet I was like a mute abroad.

187
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:22,420
Just after one year,

188
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:24,380
my English was

189
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:26,700
good enough to perform Shakespeare’s plays.

190
00:13:27,140 --> 00:13:28,860
Am I awesome?

191
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:31,300
You studied abroad

192
00:13:31,300 --> 00:13:32,660
and traveled around the world,

193
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:35,340
while I’m a lass from the small place Fan Village.

194
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:37,780
So you despise me.

195
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:40,860
How come you talk about it again?

196
00:13:41,260 --> 00:13:42,620
That’s not what I meant.

197
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:47,980
I’m telling you about my past.

198
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,180
At that time

199
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:51,820
I not only played drama,

200
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,460
but also wrote scripts myself.

201
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:55,180
The heroine in my play

202
00:13:55,300 --> 00:13:56,380
is a tailor. She...

203
00:13:56,380 --> 00:13:57,900
I’m not interested in your heroine.

204
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:00,740
It has nothing to do with me.

205
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:02,980
You were forced to go home

206
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:04,780
while you studied abroad.

207
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:06,860
You are not able to do what you like.

208
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:09,500
Shuiyun Theater is

209
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:11,220
the place where you have fun.

210
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:12,620
Then go ahead.

211
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:14,540
As long as you have a good time

212
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:15,460
and you are happy,

213
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:16,300
I promise you.

214
00:14:16,580 --> 00:14:17,580
But remember this.

215
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:19,060
You can play anything outside,

216
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:20,500
but don’t have any other woman

217
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:21,620
or any bastard.

218
00:14:22,140 --> 00:14:23,940
This family will not accept that.

219
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:35,140
Although Jiang Rongshou is wicked,

220
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:36,740
he is an old man.

221
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,180
I can’t beat him on the ground, can I?

222
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:41,180
So I went out and have fun.

223
00:14:41,460 --> 00:14:43,180
Out of sight, out of mind.

224
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,980
Jiang Rongshou

225
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:49,820
was bossy and domineering.

226
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:52,660
Now he is a senior,

227
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:54,740
and gets more ostentatious.

228
00:14:55,380 --> 00:14:57,380
You have no one to rely on in Peking.

229
00:14:57,380 --> 00:14:59,100
He bullies you.

230
00:15:02,220 --> 00:15:04,740
You need a senior to help you.

231
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:07,620
Mr. Shang is young.

232
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:11,060
You need a backer to support you in Peking.

233
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,540
Yes.

234
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:15,740
My uncle

235
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:17,500
bullies us for he is

236
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,700
our senior.

237
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:23,580
Sadly, the former leader Mr. Shang died too early.

238
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:25,820
I can do nothing for that.

239
00:15:26,620 --> 00:15:28,420
My father picked me up at the roadside,

240
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,740
but I can’t pick up a father at the roadside.

241
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:47,260
It’s your luck.

242
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,060
You have a father in front of you.

243
00:15:58,580 --> 00:16:01,220
Chen Renxiang, you want to die?

244
00:16:01,380 --> 00:16:03,020
I can be your father.

245
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,060
Don’t.

246
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:06,460
I dare not be your father.

247
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:07,300
My longevity will be shortened.

248
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:09,500
Mr. Shang.

249
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:12,580
If you don’t mind,

250
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:16,540
how about you take me as your senior?

251
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:20,060
You... Well...

252
00:16:21,220 --> 00:16:22,380
What do you mean?

253
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:25,260
I want you to be my godson.

254
00:16:26,140 --> 00:16:27,300
What do you think?

255
00:16:30,380 --> 00:16:31,980
Don’t hesitate.

256
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:35,340
Mr. Liu is a big shot.

257
00:16:36,220 --> 00:16:38,220
You call him father today.

258
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,460
Who dares to bully you casually

259
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:41,660
in the future?

260
00:16:42,180 --> 00:16:42,940
Mr. Shang.

261
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:44,940
Not everyone

262
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:47,220
has the bliss like this.

263
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:48,060
Right.

264
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:50,140
You called us gentlemen just now.

265
00:16:50,420 --> 00:16:52,700
Now you may call us first brother, second brother.

266
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:54,540
I’m your third brother.

267
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,740
I’m your fourth brother.

268
00:16:56,380 --> 00:16:56,980
Fifth brother.

269
00:16:57,500 --> 00:16:58,220
Sixth brother.

270
00:17:25,780 --> 00:17:27,060
Xirui.

271
00:17:28,580 --> 00:17:30,180
As an opera performer,

272
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:33,540
you shall adhere to rules as an artist.

273
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,980
You are my child now.

274
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:39,460
The world is dangerous.

275
00:17:40,220 --> 00:17:42,580
I will be your amulet

276
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:45,660
and suppress the evilness for you.

277
00:17:47,060 --> 00:17:50,380
But you have to promise me this.

278
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:55,580
If you dare to do evil

279
00:17:55,780 --> 00:17:57,500
in my name,

280
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:01,940
I will not spare you.

281
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:04,620
Father, thanks for your appreciation.

282
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:07,020
I will be cautious in the future,

283
00:18:07,660 --> 00:18:08,780
and dare not act rashly.

284
00:18:14,940 --> 00:18:15,780
Good.

285
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:17,700
Good.

286
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:28,180
This is

287
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:30,900
my gift to you.

288
00:18:32,620 --> 00:18:36,740
I wish you could be happy and safe.

289
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:47,620
Why does Liu Hanyun

290
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:49,220
have so many godsons?

291
00:18:50,740 --> 00:18:52,220
He is old,

292
00:18:52,540 --> 00:18:53,820
yet has no son.

293
00:18:53,820 --> 00:18:55,620
Having some godsons for fun.

294
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:01,380
You have a powerful father now.

295
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:02,940
How do you feel?

296
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:06,340
I haven’t come back to normal yet.

297
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:09,620
How come I have a father all of a sudden?

298
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:11,860
When we just arrived in Nanking,

299
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:13,580
Matchmaker was performed in the theater.

300
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:14,460
Pa! Pa! Pa!

301
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:16,020
You answered

302
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:17,140
‘yes, yes’.

303
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:18,940
Now,

304
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:20,100
you are not a father,

305
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:21,940
but a son of Liu.

306
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:24,060
It’s a punishment for you.

307
00:19:24,620 --> 00:19:26,020
Didn’t you egg him on?

308
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:28,460
Don't worry.

309
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:30,700
My father will talk with you from Heaven.

310
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:31,820
I am not afraid.

311
00:19:32,780 --> 00:19:34,380
He becomes the peer of a high-ranking official.

312
00:19:35,820 --> 00:19:36,940
He should thank me

313
00:19:36,940 --> 00:19:38,020
for gracing him.

314
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:39,620
It’s his honor.

315
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:40,460
You know that?

316
00:19:42,220 --> 00:19:44,500
Alright. You have a father now.

317
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:47,140
Let’s go to Shanghai.

318
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:48,540
Let me go to Shanghai with you?

319
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:50,020
Will you get me a godmother?

320
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:51,500
Go alone.

321
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:53,220
Where will you go?

322
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:55,460
Go home.

323
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:03,260
The son of chairman of Opera Association comes.

324
00:20:03,260 --> 00:20:04,740
He said he has big news.

325
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:05,820
What news?

326
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:10,300
Shang Xirui’s scandal. So...

327
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:13,020
Let him get out right away.

328
00:20:13,220 --> 00:20:14,060
OK. OK.

329
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:15,220
Come back.

330
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:18,220
I don’t want this news

331
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:20,100
be on other newspapers either.

332
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:21,180
Understand?

333
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:22,180
Yes, Yes.

334
00:20:26,020 --> 00:20:28,500
Mr. Du. Satisfied?

335
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:31,860
Yes.

336
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:39,820
The news Cao Guixiu made troubles in Jiang family
on New Year’s Eve

337
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:43,780
and Jiang Xirui relied on backer and disrespected his seniors

338
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:45,220
are all withdrawn by me.

339
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:49,780
Should you hand in your manuscripts?

340
00:20:52,580 --> 00:20:54,340
You occupy many pen names

341
00:20:54,340 --> 00:20:55,860
and pages.

342
00:20:56,140 --> 00:20:57,780
You must write for us.

343
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:01,220
Those editors are crazy.

344
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:04,380
I want you to know

345
00:21:04,620 --> 00:21:05,660
between me

346
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:07,700
and news,

347
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:10,620
which is more important.

348
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,820
Yes, yes.

349
00:21:16,140 --> 00:21:17,260
Without me,

350
00:21:17,260 --> 00:21:19,580
your news is nothing.

351
00:21:20,580 --> 00:21:22,380
It’s all my fault.

352
00:21:23,620 --> 00:21:25,260
But if you had told me

353
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:27,180
that you are Mu Shuang’er

354
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:28,860
and you are Lin Zhengyang,

355
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:30,380
this wouldn’t have happened.

356
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:35,300
This is interesting.

357
00:21:36,580 --> 00:21:37,020
I

358
00:21:37,020 --> 00:21:38,260
like your serial martial arts novel

359
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:41,460
Sword Seeking in Mount Hua very much.

360
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:45,540
And the critical article about Zuo Yidong.

361
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:46,700
That is also good.

362
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:50,300
Are my articles good?

363
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:52,780
Yes, of course.

364
00:21:56,260 --> 00:21:57,220
Mr. Du.

365
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:00,700
I’m wondering

366
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:02,900
to open a special column

367
00:22:03,420 --> 00:22:04,980
in the society page for you.

368
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:06,380
You may write about

369
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:08,500
essays about civil life.

370
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,380
Do you have interest?

371
00:22:14,980 --> 00:22:16,460
Depend on your performance.

372
00:22:18,020 --> 00:22:18,820
OK.

373
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:22,500
The payment isn't a problem.

374
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:26,900
You are loyal

375
00:22:27,460 --> 00:22:29,300
to Mr. Shang.

376
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:32,100
I haven’t seen any writer

377
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:34,100
who is so devoted to a performer.

378
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:36,340
You are no ordinary.

379
00:22:37,140 --> 00:22:38,620
Not to mention Mr. Shang.

380
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:40,740
Mr. Shang is no ordinary for sure.

381
00:22:41,020 --> 00:22:42,620
My eyes are keen

382
00:22:42,780 --> 00:22:44,540
like searchlights.

383
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:47,580
If I work in glaze factory,

384
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:49,260
all the business in this street

385
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:51,260
will be mine.

386
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:53,180
I can’t agree more.

387
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:54,860
Mr. Du.

388
00:22:55,140 --> 00:22:56,540
I am sincere.

389
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:58,060
What do you think?

390
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:03,020
OK.

391
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:07,820
One article a week.

392
00:23:07,820 --> 00:23:09,100
One thousand words in one article.

393
00:23:09,100 --> 00:23:11,140
No one word more.

394
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:12,860
As you said.

395
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:14,380
Mr. Du.

396
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:16,500
I’d like to treat you for dinner

397
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:19,060
to learn some literal arts.

398
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,820
Mr. Xue comes for meal?

399
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:24,700
Fine.

400
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:26,620
Give me the payment first.

401
00:23:26,620 --> 00:23:27,660
This meal is on me.

402
00:23:28,340 --> 00:23:29,900
Well...

403
00:23:29,900 --> 00:23:30,940
You have no money

404
00:23:30,940 --> 00:23:32,220
just after New Year?

405
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:34,860
Fine. Fine.

406
00:23:38,460 --> 00:23:39,940
You treat me for meal,

407
00:23:40,940 --> 00:23:42,620
but the money is still mine.

408
00:23:42,780 --> 00:23:47,260
As it goes, nothing comes for free.

409
00:24:05,660 --> 00:24:07,060
I didn’t see that collar button before.

410
00:24:07,700 --> 00:24:08,580
New?

411
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:11,020
From my brother?

412
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,300
An old trick.

413
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:15,180
When he makes me upset,

414
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:16,900
he’ll give me flowers, candies,

415
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:18,020
or jewelry.

416
00:24:18,460 --> 00:24:21,300
That’s called romance. You know?

417
00:24:22,580 --> 00:24:23,980
You have new jewelry.

418
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:25,980
Go shopping with me.

419
00:24:26,260 --> 00:24:27,860
No one sees your beauty at home.

420
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:30,860
The mall

421
00:24:30,860 --> 00:24:32,340
is too crowded.

422
00:24:33,020 --> 00:24:34,100
I was forced

423
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:35,140
to go out the other day.

424
00:24:35,140 --> 00:24:36,620
I don’t like to be seen in public.

425
00:24:36,900 --> 00:24:38,260
You may go alone.

426
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:40,540
Do you need a car, ma’am?

427
00:24:40,980 --> 00:24:42,580
Mr. Cheng drove the car away.

428
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,500
I never use car in the daytime.

429
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:40,540
Is it today?

430
00:25:41,380 --> 00:25:42,780
Is the date wrong?

431
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:49,660
My gosh.

432
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:52,620
You scared me.

433
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:54,820
Why are you dressed like this?

434
00:25:56,020 --> 00:25:57,660
Mr. Cheng. I’m hungry.

435
00:25:57,660 --> 00:25:59,220
Let me tell you when eating.

436
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:01,180
I reserved meal in the tavern for you.

437
00:26:01,180 --> 00:26:02,620
The men of Shuiyun Theater have arrived there.

438
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:04,060
I volunteered

439
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:06,980
to come and be your driver.

440
00:26:07,940 --> 00:26:08,860
Let’s go.

441
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:13,180
What?

442
00:26:14,220 --> 00:26:16,420
Did you regard Liu Hanyun as your godfather?

443
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:17,900
I have no idea

444
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:19,300
why the news spread so fast.

445
00:26:19,300 --> 00:26:21,780
People in the train saw me like a clown.

446
00:26:22,060 --> 00:26:23,620
They even surrounded me.

447
00:26:23,620 --> 00:26:24,940
So I disguised.

448
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:26,860
I can’t believe you are also deceived by me.

449
00:26:27,260 --> 00:26:29,060
Hey, who is Liu Hanyun?

450
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:30,500
Who is Liu Hanyun?

451
00:26:30,740 --> 00:26:31,460
Right.

452
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,340
Who is Liu Hanyun?

453
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:35,060
Don’t you know Liu Hanyun?

454
00:26:35,060 --> 00:26:35,580
No.

455
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:37,500
He is an official beside the president

456
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:39,380
in charge of life and death.

457
00:26:39,660 --> 00:26:40,500
Really?

458
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:42,260
In that case,

459
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:44,980
our leader is the son of the high-ranking official.

460
00:26:45,620 --> 00:26:46,500
Congratulations, leader.

461
00:26:46,780 --> 00:26:47,660
Congratulations, leader.

462
00:26:48,020 --> 00:26:49,540
-Congratulations, leader.
-Congratulations, leader.

463
00:26:49,540 --> 00:26:50,900
No one dares to bully Shuiyun Theater anymore.

464
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:52,260
-That’s right.
-Right.

465
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:53,260
Right.

466
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:54,180
Right.

467
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:55,620
Mr. Cheng.

468
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:58,020
What do you think of this matter?

469
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:01,260
Liu Hanyun is in Nanking all the time.

470
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:03,140
I don’t know much about him.

471
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:06,340
As for his godsons,

472
00:27:06,620 --> 00:27:08,620
they’re successful young men in all industries

473
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:10,260
who have no backer.

474
00:27:10,620 --> 00:27:12,700
Liu has gathered almost all of them.

475
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:14,060
From this point,

476
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:17,580
I don’t believe Liu Hanyun

477
00:27:17,860 --> 00:27:19,180
isn’t ambitious.

478
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:22,020
Politicians are complicated.

479
00:27:22,220 --> 00:27:23,660
You should stay out of it, Mr. Shang.

480
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:26,860
I didn't think so much.

481
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:28,220
We talked and then

482
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:29,300
became his godson.

483
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:31,980
I don’t want to be bullied by Jiang family.

484
00:27:32,580 --> 00:27:34,580
The telegram and phone call are convenient.

485
00:27:34,900 --> 00:27:37,420
You should call me

486
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:38,660
and talk with me first.

487
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:49,180
Leader. You missed a good show

488
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:51,940
these days.

489
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:53,780
What show?

490
00:27:53,780 --> 00:27:55,220
Mr. Du told me

491
00:27:55,220 --> 00:27:57,220
Mr. Cheng avenged you

492
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:59,740
and made a scene in Jiang family on New Year’s Eve.

493
00:27:59,740 --> 00:28:01,220
You didn’t see it.

494
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,820
Jiang Rongshou was

495
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:04,660
frightened the life out of him.

496
00:28:04,660 --> 00:28:06,300
He dares not to bully you again.

497
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:07,660
Right. Right.

498
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:09,540
Is it true, Mr. Cheng?

499
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:15,060
I’m happy. Great.

500
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:18,140
You should have gone there yourself.

501
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:19,220
Disgrace him face to face.

502
00:28:19,420 --> 00:28:20,700
That would be exciting.

503
00:28:21,340 --> 00:28:22,180
-Come on.
-Go ahead.

504
00:28:22,180 --> 00:28:23,700
I won't. It's annoying.

505
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:25,620
What’s wrong?

506
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,500
I recognized a father in vain.

507
00:28:28,740 --> 00:28:30,140
Not in vain.

508
00:28:30,860 --> 00:28:32,860
You must have got a gift from him.

509
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:33,540
You’re right.

510
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:35,500
Liu Hanyun gave me such a big Ruyi.

511
00:28:36,500 --> 00:28:38,220
You still call him Liu Hanyun?

512
00:28:38,220 --> 00:28:39,980
Call him father.

513
00:28:41,380 --> 00:28:42,580
You take advantage me.

514
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,940
Braised fillet in brown sauce.

515
00:28:44,620 --> 00:28:46,060
Roasted goose.

516
00:28:46,660 --> 00:28:48,340
-We have more?
-Who ordered these?

517
00:28:48,460 --> 00:28:49,740
-No.
-Who ordered these?

518
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:54,180
Braised pork shoulder?

519
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:57,100
Mr. Shang. Mr. Cheng.

520
00:28:57,500 --> 00:28:58,580
Hello, everybody.

521
00:28:58,580 --> 00:29:00,260
Mr. Niu. Mr. Niu. Mr. Niu.

522
00:29:00,260 --> 00:29:01,260
Mr. Niu. Here.

523
00:29:01,260 --> 00:29:01,980
Sit here.

524
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:02,740
Let’s drink.

525
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:03,180
Mr. Niu.

526
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:04,220
No, thanks.

527
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,220
You know.

528
00:29:07,420 --> 00:29:09,420
Those gentlemen from Opera Association

529
00:29:09,420 --> 00:29:10,500
are also here.

530
00:29:10,900 --> 00:29:11,980
They hear that you are here,

531
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:13,220
so they come to visit you.

532
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:16,060
Would you like to meet them?

533
00:29:18,460 --> 00:29:20,300
Yes, of course.

534
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,020
OK.

535
00:29:21,620 --> 00:29:23,300
Gentlemen, come in.

536
00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:24,700
These old men?

537
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:25,620
How come they are here?

538
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:26,420
What are they doing here?

539
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:27,580
Look.

540
00:29:27,580 --> 00:29:29,020
Such a big worm.

541
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:30,460
Mr. Shang.

542
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:32,500
We feel sorry for what happened

543
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:33,260
in the Opera Association

544
00:29:33,260 --> 00:29:34,340
before the New Year.

545
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:36,300
We didn't see you at your home.

546
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:36,980
We heard that

547
00:29:36,980 --> 00:29:38,300
You went to other places for the New Year.

548
00:29:38,420 --> 00:29:39,900
Jiang is a senior.

549
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:41,300
In that situation,

550
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:43,100
we couldn’t say anything.

551
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:45,900
Mr. Shang. Don’t blame us.

552
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:47,260
We all know well

553
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:48,820
you did nothing wrong.

554
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:49,260
Yes.

555
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:50,380
My troupe

556
00:29:50,700 --> 00:29:52,980
will be changed into the contract system too.

557
00:29:52,980 --> 00:29:55,140
Right. We didn't say anything,

558
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:56,900
but we all support Mr. Shang.

559
00:29:56,900 --> 00:29:57,340
Yes.

560
00:29:57,340 --> 00:29:59,180
Sorry, Mr. Shang.

561
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:02,540
Not at all. You are

562
00:30:02,860 --> 00:30:04,580
junior to Jiang indeed.

563
00:30:04,740 --> 00:30:06,340
You can’t speak up for me,

564
00:30:06,540 --> 00:30:08,500
but I clearly know your kindness

565
00:30:08,660 --> 00:30:10,180
to me.

566
00:30:10,300 --> 00:30:11,500
Thank you, gentlemen.

567
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:13,980
You tolerate us.

568
00:30:13,980 --> 00:30:15,580
We feel much relieved.

569
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:16,620
Yes. Yes.

570
00:30:20,980 --> 00:30:21,900
Well... Well...

571
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:24,580
Mr. Cheng. I’ve heard a lot about you.

572
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:26,620
Mr. Niu.

573
00:30:27,580 --> 00:30:29,060
I’m here for meal,

574
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:31,260
not for operas.

575
00:30:31,980 --> 00:30:33,740
So many performers are here.

576
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:38,180
Sorry, Mr. Cheng.

577
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:40,460
