Your script is good for sure.

709
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:39,220
Don’t. Don’t.

710
00:37:40,060 --> 00:37:42,220
I have to put this first.

711
00:37:43,060 --> 00:37:43,980
Say it.

712
00:37:46,980 --> 00:37:47,980
First,

713
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,900
