730
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:32,020
The original of all operas.

731
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:35,380
How come no one likes it now?

732
00:38:39,020 --> 00:38:40,380
Listen.

733
00:38:40,900 --> 00:38:42,220
Performers

734
