841
00:42:36,140 --> 00:42:37,780
Thank you, lord.

842
00:42:37,780 --> 00:42:40,620
Then I will come with Mr. Shang.

843
00:42:40,900 --> 00:42:41,580
OK.

844
00:42:41,940 --> 00:42:43,420
Let’s make a deal then.

845
00:42:43,700 --> 00:42:45,020
See you around.

846
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:47,100
Tea is coming.

847
00:42:48,060 --> 00:42:49,100
You may

848
00:42:49,100 --> 00:42:50,460
