849
00:42:50,940 --> 00:42:52,420
Alright. No need to send me out.

850
00:42:52,820 --> 00:42:53,500
I’m leaving.

851
00:42:54,580 --> 00:42:55,940
-Take care, Lord.
-Take care, Lord.

852
00:42:55,940 --> 00:42:56,620
OK.

853
00:42:56,620 --> 00:42:57,980
Take care.

854
00:42:58,660 --> 00:42:59,540
Leader, have a taste.

855
00:43:03,100 --> 00:43:04,340
Mr. Du. Try it.

856
00:43:08,620 --> 00:43:09,620
What taste is it?

857
00:43:09,900 --> 00:43:11,020
What tea is it?

858
00:43:13,260 --> 00:43:14,620
Should I

859
00:43:15,900 --> 00:43:17,220
