863
00:43:25,940 --> 00:43:28,500
The election will be held in two months.

864
00:43:28,700 --> 00:43:31,460
You want to avenge for your father.

865
00:43:32,620 --> 00:43:34,700
If you sing Kun opera,

866
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,860
